{"tid":964510,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"讀完ive升大學疑問","createTime":"2019-01-01T11:02:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-03T17:42:49.000Z","uid":229277,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7a863af14c0e5be886675fff592967f002eb34da","tid":964510,"uid":229277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T11:02:46.000Z","msg":"幫朋友問埋<br />\n我係讀ive既hd課程<br />\n我朋友係讀理工既副學士<br />\n我想問一下如果報大學既話係咪報第1年既課程?<br />\n同埋如果成績好好既話有無機會直接上第2/3年?<br />\n以前中學老師話係有機會可以直上<br />\n但唔係有無fake我 <br />\n之前我都比佢fake左 所以讀左ive"},{"pid":"df2d100f45dc6025a080a8d005dd431f90de0950","tid":964510,"uid":194824,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T12:59:40.000Z","msg":"有分senior or junior year entry 架<br />\n<br />\n大佬呀 google 左先啦<br />\n<br />\nNon-jupas"},{"pid":"c822d2825bf4ea093c6212d16efecd62110c3ae7","tid":964510,"uid":213441,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T13:01:04.000Z","msg":"無 要考多次dse"},{"pid":"79c8d48c3156dea884a020b7ae27502fa1518ba6","tid":964510,"uid":191296,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T00:40:18.000Z","msg":"Poly有副學士？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw poly親生仔升返poly好易收<br />\nPoly親生仔唔係指hkcc，係指poly本校自己嘅course<br />\n<br />\n不過樓主同樓主朋友google又唔識，追non ju post又唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n1234年都冇機會升<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64cdef994b945e8fc3b56ebc9ae405d3e56636ef","tid":964510,"uid":28451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T01:41:55.000Z","msg":"學校有老師唔問走黎連登問<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82ba569e52617b681e62dfdf44d82071d5afcdc5","tid":964510,"uid":163024,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T17:27:34.000Z","msg":"1)想入POLY要睇你本身讀咩HD，如果理工科會易入啲<br />\n2)IVE仔一般都係經Non-Jupus報Senior Entry(Year3)，如果你想應該可以入返Year1。一般讀IVE第二年九月份POLY就會開始Admission，快嘅話11月就會叫你去Interview，12月就會收到Offer<br />\n3)POLY CC易入就一定，我報果科有個CC GPA3.1X都收咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 IVE IT科GPA3.9 手上有一個POLY Offer，但唔會去紅磡技校<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d8cb062173b3b662c5bc659a3db64be6f9944fc","tid":964510,"uid":163024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T17:31:45.000Z","msg":"你睇清楚自己咩料先好去報，IVE大把你呢啲Sem雄心壯志想入大學跟住Year就炒曬車嘅辣殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nPOLY CGPA3.4以上派Interview<br />\nCGPA3.7以上收Early Round<br />\nCPGA3.5就等Main Round<br />\n<br />\n一般3月就收完7成生，主要睇Year1成績<br />\nbtw你google都唔識就<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a2c7aa316c1a06ec2c80abdba2aff2f2d29d790","tid":964510,"uid":193011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82ba569e52617b681e62dfdf44d82071d5afcdc5","tid":964510,"uid":163024,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T17:27:34.000Z","msg":"1)想入POLY要睇你本身讀咩HD，如果理工科會易入啲<br />\n2)IVE仔一般都係經Non-Jupus報Senior Entry(Year3)，如果你想應該可以入返Year1。一般讀IVE第二年九月份POLY就會開始Admission，快嘅話11月就會叫你去Interview，12月就會收到Offer<br />\n3)POLY CC易入就一定，我報果科有個CC GPA3.1X都收咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 IVE IT科GPA3.9 手上有一個POLY Offer，但唔會去紅磡技校<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T17:41:24.000Z","msg":"今年ust cs收少左一半人，cu位又少，呢兩間都已經出左first round,身邊又無咩人reject 。巴打小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2afe845e7f87b1e585a8a31ec8e93d82e4ef6de","tid":964510,"uid":163024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a2c7aa316c1a06ec2c80abdba2aff2f2d29d790","tid":964510,"uid":193011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82ba569e52617b681e62dfdf44d82071d5afcdc5","tid":964510,"uid":163024,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T17:27:34.000Z","msg":"1)想入POLY